{"id":"api/animations/useAnimation","title":"useAnimation","contents":"\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/animations\", \"name\": \"@angular/animations\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/animations/useAnimation\", \"name\": \"useAnimation\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/animations\">@angular/animations</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts?message=docs(animations)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1637-L1663\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts#L1637-L1663\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"useanimation\">useAnimation<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/animations/useAnimation#useanimation\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">啟動一個使用 <code><a href=\"api/animations/animation\" class=\"code-anchor\">animation</a>()</code> 函式建立的可複用動畫。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Starts a reusable animation that is created using the <code><a href=\"api/animations/animation\" class=\"code-anchor\">animation</a>()</code> function.</p>\n\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  \n\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/animations/useAnimation\" class=\"code-anchor\">useAnimation</a></span>(<a href=\"api/animations/animation\" class=\"code-anchor\">animation</a>: <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationReferenceMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationReferenceMetadata</a>, options: <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationOptions</a> = null): <a href=\"api/animations/AnimationAnimateRefMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationAnimateRefMetadata</a></code-example>\n\n  \n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"引數\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code><a href=\"api/animations/animation\" class=\"code-anchor\">animation</a></code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/animations/AnimationReferenceMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationReferenceMetadata</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-result=\"on\">要啟動的可複用動畫。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The reusable animation to start.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>options</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/animations/AnimationOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationOptions</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-result=\"on\">一個配置物件，它包含一個啟動動畫之前的延遲值，和一些由開發人員定義的改寫引數值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">An options object that can contain a delay value for the start of\nthe animation, and additional override values for developer-defined parameters.</p>\n\n        <div no-translate=\"\">可選. 預設值是 `null`.</div>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h6>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">一個包含動畫引數的物件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/animations/AnimationAnimateRefMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">AnimationAnimateRefMetadata</a></code>: An object that contains the animation parameters.</p>\n\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n</div>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/animations\n - api/animations/AnimationAnimateRefMetadata\n - api/animations/AnimationMetadataType\n - api/animations/AnimationOptions\n - api/animations/AnimationReferenceMetadata\n - api/animations/animation\n - guide/animations\n - guide/reusable-animations\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/animations\n - api/animations/AnimationAnimateRefMetadata\n - api/animations/AnimationOptions\n - api/animations/AnimationReferenceMetadata\n - api/animations/animation\n - api/animations/useAnimation#useanimation\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts?message=docs(animations)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L1637-L1663\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/animations/src/animation_metadata.ts#L1637-L1663\n-->"}